<title>USA: Advanced Polymer sets share rights plan.</title>
<headline>Advanced Polymer sets share rights plan.</headline>
<dateline>REDWOOD, Calif. 1996-08-21</dateline>
<text>
<p>Advanced Polymer Systems Inc said on Wednesday that its board had approved the adoption of a shareholder rights plan to assure stockholders fair value and equal treatment in the event of any proposed takeover of the company.</p>
<p>The company said this plan is not in response to any known effort to acquire control of it.</p>
